metadata.name: Cute? No, I'm Cool.
metadata.description:
My good friend Luv has created the cutest character.
Her name is Luv-chan.

She shows many cute sides in different places.
I wanted to see a different side of her.
She wears a variety of cute clothes.
I wanted to see a different side of her.

I am good at cool illustrations. So what kind of expression does she show us?

I let her wear the fashions I wear.
This is my other answer to her showing many cute aspects.

My illustration is featured as a guest in Luv's illustration book.
Luv: @luvluv_eth
